---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="2025 Annual Report | Wasatch Wildlife Alliance"
  description="Wasatch Wildlife Alliance's 2025 Annual Report highlights a year of record impact in conservation, education, and community engagement."
>
  <article class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <a href="/news/" class="text-forest-600 hover:text-forest-800 font-semibold text-sm flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-8 transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18" />
        </svg>
        Back to News
      </a>

      <span class="inline-block bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">Report</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
        2025 Annual Report: A Year of Record Impact
      </h1>
      <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mb-8">January 5, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none text-stone-700 leading-relaxed space-y-5">
        <p>
          2025 was our most impactful year yet. Thanks to the generosity of our donors and the dedication of our 1,200+ volunteers, Wasatch Wildlife Alliance achieved record milestones across every program area.
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-4">Key Achievements</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><strong>2,500 acres</strong> of new habitat protected or restored, bringing our total to over 15,000 acres</li>
          <li><strong>12,000+ native plants</strong> installed across 8 restoration sites</li>
          <li><strong>42 species</strong> under active monitoring through our wildlife survey program</li>
          <li><strong>8,200 students</strong> participated in Jr. Ranger and other education programs</li>
          <li><strong>25,000+ volunteer hours</strong> contributed by community members</li>
          <li><strong>$1.2M</strong> raised in donations and grants, with 92% going directly to programs</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-4">Looking Ahead to 2026</h2>
        <p>
          In the coming year, we plan to expand our restoration work into new watersheds, launch a community science app for wildlife sighting reports, and grow our Jr. Ranger program to 45 partner schools. None of this would be possible without your support.
        </p>
        <p>
          Read the full report or <a href="/donate/" class="text-forest-600 hover:text-forest-800 font-semibold underline">make a donation</a> to help us build on this momentum.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-stone-200 mt-12 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-4">
        <a href="/news/" class="text-forest-600 hover:text-forest-800 font-semibold text-sm flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18" />
          </svg>
          All News
        </a>
        <a href="/donate/" class="btn-donate !py-2.5 !px-5 !text-sm">
          Support Our Mission
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="h-16 lg:hidden"></div>
</BaseLayout>
